?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOgVRV3.jpg&h=901d0580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eBAGNup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeBAGNup.jpg&h=42b3a696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2A5LuHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2A5LuHK.jpg&h=2e1887ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cda78203e38fe384f81804225131a4c23593e584","tid":2003691,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:59:35.000Z","msg":"警暴一日未除，香港一日不寧"},{"pid":"16df63df5722c48802ec87d87576f0f8077fba9e","tid":2003691,"uid":16903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"毛澤東語錄：<br />\n<br />\n「我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」<br />\n<br />\n〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉，1939年5月26日"},{"pid":"890c15d27fdfe50376fe1e5c9dd7ffc4e4057250","tid":2003691,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86ecea4893cb083d3f964c5e3822de45286ecbde","tid":2003691,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209a4ad631373254b14ea3a5fd7b67edaf67e4f8","tid":2003691,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43c8c04945912ff9a2086e495bac4dc72bd142a5","tid":2003691,"uid":214644,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp grp嘅話大家自己衡量風險，除非有太空卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:41:40.000Z","msg":"agree<br 